## Setup Instructions Before Running

This code uses absolute file paths specific to the original development machine.
Before running, update these paths to match your own system.

1. Place the `P1_Project` folder anywhere on your computer.

2. Open each script in the `scripts/` folder and find the path variables near
   the top, for example:

       MVC_PATH = '/Users/wishal/Documents/P1_Project/MVC-Time-series-Forecasting'

3. Replace the path with the location of the `P1_Project` folder on your system.

4. Install dependencies: `pip install -r requirements.txt`

5. kShape clustering requires a separate environment due to a library version
   conflict. See Section 6.4 of the final report for details.
